{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_28aab787effeo1WSdYzFX3JSix","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d7559a3b100130TsLmiOUM8wvE","parts":[{"id":"prt_d7559acfd001VZfk9ZpsmhWpmC","messageID":"msg_d7559a3b100130TsLmiOUM8wvE","sessionID":"ses_28aab787effeo1WSdYzFX3JSix","type":"text","text":"## 仓库配置完成报告\n\n### 1. 环境配置\n\n**Python 版本**: 3.11.2\n\n**虚拟环境**: `/workspace/.venv`\n\n**已安装的主要依赖**:\n- fastapi-pagination (0.15.12, editable)\n- fastapi (0.135.3)\n- pydantic (2.12.5)\n- sqlalchemy (2.0.49)\n- pytest (9.0.3)\n- pytest-asyncio (1.3.0)\n- httpx (0.28.1)\n- aiosqlite (0.22.1)\n- asyncpg (0.31.0)\n- motor (3.7.1)\n- beanie (2.1.0)\n- odmantic (1.1.0)\n- ruff (0.15.10)\n- ty (0.0.29)\n\n### 2. 验证结果\n\n#### 核心测试 (tests/ 目录，不含 ext)\n```\n488 passed in 1.67s\n```\n**状态**: ✅ 全部通过\n\n#### 扩展测试 (tests/ext/)\n- **test_dummy.py, test_utils.py**: 5/5 通过 ✅\n- **test_sqlalchemy.py (SQLite sync)**: 22/22 通过 ✅\n- **test_sqlalchemy.py (PostgreSQL)**: 672 errors (需要 PostgreSQL 服务) ❌\n- **test_sqlalchemy.py (SQLite async cursor)**: 8 failures (sqlakeyset 异步兼容性问题) ❌\n\n#### 代码质量检查\n- **Ruff lint**: ✅ All checks passed\n- **Ty type check (core modules)**: ✅ All checks passed\n\n### 3. 失败原因说明\n\n1. **PostgreSQL 相关测试失败**: 需要运行 PostgreSQL 服务，当前环境未提供\n2. **SQLite async cursor 测试失败**: `TypeError: object ChunkedIteratorResult can't be used in 'await' expression` - 这是 sqlakeyset 库与当前 SQLAlchemy 版本的异步兼容性问题\n\n### 4. 关键操作记录\n\n```bash\n# 创建虚拟环境\npython3 -m venv .venv\n\n# 安装项目依赖\npip install -e \".[sqlalchemy]\"\npip install pytest pytest-asyncio pytest-cov httpx asgi-lifespan Faker dirty-equals\npip install aiosqlite asyncpg motor pymongo google-cloud-firestore cassandra-driver\npip install beanie odmantic ruff ty\n\n# 运行核心测试\npytest tests/ --ignore=tests/ext/\n\n# 代码检查\nruff check fastapi_pagination/\nty check fastapi_pagination/ --exclude 'fastapi_pagination/ext/*'\n```\n\n### 5. 结论\n\n**核心功能验证**: ✅ 通过\n\nfastapi-pagination 库的核心功能（488 个测试）全部通过，代码 lint 和类型检查也通过。需要外部数据库（PostgreSQL、MongoDB 等）的扩展测试因环境限制无法运行，但 SQLite 同步测试通过，证明 SQLAlchemy 扩展基本功能正常。","time":{"start":1775790316946,"end":1775790316946}}]}
